{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_01","textHome":"我只不过是带着照相机拍照的人而已。@我是不会那么简单就成为拍摄对象的哦。@那么，不要在意我，去别的地方就行了。@我拍了很多别人反感的东西，敌人也很多。@在被人当做我的同伴之前，你还是离开比较好，@不过你要是想跟着我的话，就要做好觉悟哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_17","textHome":"要写报道的话就需要证词对吧？@但是也有看了证据也沉默不语的家伙，@这种时候就只能自己取材了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_18","textHome":"我做了很多伤害对方的事，所以敌人很多。@不过，因为我而获得拯救的人也很多。@实际上，也有人在暗中帮助我。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":400}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_19","textHome":"观鸟报势不可挡。@过去或是今后都是如此！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_20","textHome":"这样子，收集证据的计划就完成了。@不要小看我哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_21","textHome":"就算有着无数能够按下快门的机会，@也会由于技术和体力的不足而错失。@我，已经不想体会这样的遗憾了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_22","textHome":"哪里都不存在什么眼不见心不烦。@善恶混杂的现实之中，也一定存在着真相。@如果不能认同这一点，是得不到我的认同的。@就算这只是我的自我满足也好。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":1}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3046_00_23","textHome":"真相要在一个人的手中持续发酵。@如果不这样的话是不行的。@如果不是一个人来做，真相就会被其他人歪曲。@我考虑过了，所以今后无论发生什么，@我也要一个人战斗。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":304600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304600}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.e